OL,3,CNightclubs to close in Portsmouth and
OL,4,CWindsor as chain enters administration
OL,6,FChairman of Rekom UK, Peter Marks
OL,7,Fcommented: "We have made every effort
OL,8,Fto redeploy staff across the business
OL,9,Fwhere possible and we're pleased to
OL,10,Fhave saved around 1000 jobs.
OL,12,F"Regrettably, however, the reduced
OL,13,Festate meant it was inevitable that we
OL,14,Fwould have to make some redundancies.
OL,16,F"We have informed all colleagues
OL,17,Fwithin the organisation of the
OL,18,Funfortunate developments that have
OL,19,Ftaken place over the last 18 days.
