OL,6,F"Accordingly, the administrators have
OL,7,Fhad to close 17 sites because the
OL,8,Fcommercial prospects of the affected
OL,9,Fbusinesses render them unviable to
OL,10,Fcontinue to operate resulting in
OL,11,Fapproximately 471 redundancies.
OL,13,F"The Grant Thornton team will work
OL,14,Fwith the employees affected to support
OL,15,Fthem through this process.
